Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest build

Purpose:
  Build derived graph or summary data from imported source.

Usage:
  spinedigest build <archive.sdpub> [--stage <source|graph|summary>] [--chapter <id>] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>] [--confirm]

Contract:
  - Mutates: yes, advances archive stages.
  - LLM: graph and summary builds may call an LLM.
  - Safety: LLM-backed builds require --confirm after estimate.
  - JSON: no.

Examples:
  spinedigest estimate book.sdpub --stage summary
  spinedigest build book.sdpub --stage graph --chapter 3 --confirm
